Update from 3.0 to 3.2

- upload all files to your server
- point your browser to http://yoursite/modules/freecontent/upgrade3.0_to_3.2.php
- update the module with Xoops Admin panel

Update from previous version (2.x.x -> 3.x)

- Uninstall your old version

- Upload all files of the Freecontent 3.0 package

- Install with Xoops administration panel

Update from 3.1 to 3.2

- upload all files to your server
- update the module with Xoops Admin panel